لا يمكن لأحد في الفصل

353
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:53,600
التنافس معك.

354
00:26:55,120 --> 00:26:57,880
هونغتاي،

355
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,400
لا بد أنك تحب جيمي حقًا.

356
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:00,960
ما الذي تتحدث عنه؟ [[ن]] أوه؟

357
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:12,040
مازلت لا تدرك

358
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:16,040
ما هي نتيجة هذه الحرب؟

359
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:46,400
هل تعتقد حقًا أن

360
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:50,200
حساب الصبي العشوائي

361
00:27:51,560 --> 00:27:53,600
الذي يلعب مع كلب كل يوم

362
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:56,000
بدون أي شيء جديد أو مثير للاهتمام

363
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:05,520
يمكن أن يصل إلى 500.000 متابع بمفرده؟

364
00:28:08,120 --> 00:28:09,400
ما فعلته

365
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:11,600
جعل الجميع يركزون على جيمي

366
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:14,080
لأن البشر يحبون الصراع. [[ن]] إنهم يحبون العنف. [[ن]] أليس كذلك؟

367
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:38,560
لن أقبل ذلك!

368
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:40,120
<i>لولا كراهيتك،</i>

369
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:41,920
<i>لم يكن جيمي ليحصل على</i>
<i>هذا القدر الكبير من الاهتمام.</i>

370
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:21,280
لقد كان الأمر ممتعًا. [[ن]] ممتع جداً. [[ن]] حاربهم! [[ن]] حاربهم!

371
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:23,600
لقد وجدتك أخيرًا.

372
00:29:27,520 --> 00:29:29,840
مطارد؟

373
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,640
ولكنك لا تستطيع أن تجدني إلا عبر الإنترنت يا سكاي. [[ن]] ربما لا. [[ن]] اذهب!

374
00:29:35,120 --> 00:29:36,480
على أية حال،

375
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:39,360
في النهاية،

376
00:29:40,280 --> 00:29:42,200
تنتهي هذه الحرب بالتضحية بك.

377
00:29:42,280 --> 00:29:44,840
لكن...

378
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:48,360
لا تقلق.

379
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,320
لديك الكثير من زملائك الشهداء.

380
00:29:53,280 --> 00:29:55,600
<i>الجميع،</i>

381
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:57,080
<i>أنا آسف لأنني اختفيت مؤخرًا.</i>

382
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:12,840
<i>كنت مريضًا للغاية.</i>

383
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:14,560
<i>لكنني أتحسن الآن،</i>

384
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,000
<i>بفضل كل دعمكم.</i>

385
00:30:20,080 --> 00:30:21,160
<i>هناك شيء آخر</i>

386
00:30:25,360 --> 00:30:26,280
<i>أريد أن أخبرك الجميع.</i>

387
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:32,480
<i>مؤخرًا،</i>

388
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:33,600
<i>مجموعة من الأشخاص</i>
<i>يحاول التشهير بي.</i>

389
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,800
<i>لذلك قررت</i>

390
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,640
<i>مقاضاة كل من زعيم المجموعة،</i>

391
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:39,920
<i>الذي أعرف هويته الآن،</i>

392
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:41,280
<i>وجميع الأتباع المتورطين.</i>

393
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:44,000
<i>في البداية، ترددت،</i>
<i>لست متأكدًا مما إذا كان ينبغي علي رفع دعوى قضائية.</i>

394
00:30:56,760 --> 00:30:58,360
<i>لكن الجميع أخبرني</i>

395
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,120
<i>يجب أن أكون قدوة،</i>

396
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:02,960
<i>لذلك يجب أن أفعل هذا.</i>

397
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:03,880
<i>شكرًا جزيلا لكم جميعًا،</i>

398
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:09,600
<i>بما في ذلك الأشخاص</i>
<i>الذي أرسل لي المعلومات.</i>

399
00:31:30,120 --> 00:31:31,240
<i>هونغ يقول شكرًا لك أيضًا، أليس كذلك؟</i>

400
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:51,840
<i>شكرًا للمعجبين.</i>

401
00:31:57,840 --> 00:31:59,080
PANGSTOP

402
00:32:08,280 --> 00:32:10,000
{\an8}<i>أنت تعلم أن دعمك</i>

403
00:32:10,080 --> 00:32:11,800
<i>هو أفضل طاقة لي ولهونج، أليس كذلك؟</i>

404
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:13,160
خمسة،

405
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:18,440
أربعة،

406
00:32:20,800 --> 00:32:22,600
ثلاثة، [[ن]] اثنان، [[ن]] واحد. [[ن]] صفر. [[ن]] هونغتاي.

407
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,440
أنت ألطف مناهض للمعجبين على الإطلاق. [[ن]] هل تعلم ذلك؟ [[ن]] جيمي! جيمي!

408
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:34,880
<i>إنه جسدي.</i>

409
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:40,600
<i>يمكنني أن أفعل به ما أريد.</i>
<i>يمكنني إظهار ما أريد.</i>

410
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:44,840
<i>إنه عملي.</i>

411
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:47,040
<i>جسدي، خياري.</i>

412
00:32:47,120 --> 00:32:48,400
الفكرة بأكملها

413
00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:52,240
أن أجسادنا تنتمي إلينا

414
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:01,040
مذهلة.

415
00:33:01,120 --> 00:33:02,240
{\an8}<i>إذا لم تكن مصدر إلهام لي،</i>

416
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:08,600
<i>على الأرجح لم نكن لنحظى</i>
<i>هذا القدر من المرح الآن.</i>

417
00:33:17,120 --> 00:33:18,000
ترجمة الترجمة بواسطة: Panuwat Baikeawon [[n]]

418
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:19,120
CAN IT GET ANY WORSE THAN THIS?

419
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:20,080
EXPOSE HIM

420
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,520
Stop!

421
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:48,520
<i>Leave me alone!</i>

422
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:52,520
IT'S GOING VIRAL

423
00:33:52,600 --> 00:33:53,600
<i>Damn you!</i>

424
00:33:54,360 --> 00:33:56,000
<i>Stop!</i>

425
00:34:48,560 --> 00:34:49,760
Why?

426
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:55,240
Even though

427
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:58,160
Jamie

428
00:34:58,960 --> 00:35:00,960
lied to everyone

429
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:05,480
and didn't even adopt that dog,

430
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:10,600
why are you still helping him?

431
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,680
Helping?

432
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:16,120
Helping Jamie?

433
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:20,920
No. I wasn't helping Jamie.

434
00:35:23,160 --> 00:35:25,600
I've been helping you all along.

435
00:35:29,160 --> 00:35:30,400
Helping me?

436
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,320
Yes.

437
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:44,440
{\an8}IS IT HARD TO TAKE CARE OF A FEMALE DOG?
YOU HAVE TO BE CAREFUL, RIGHT?

438
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,880
You're trying to cover it up

439
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:54,520
because you really did
sexually harass your dog, right?

440
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:56,080
Yeah. He should be banned.

441
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:02,040
But what a surprise.

442
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:05,880
You went this far.

443
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:09,800
No one in class

444
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:13,280
can compete with you.

445
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,200
Hongtae,

446
00:36:16,720 --> 00:36:19,160
you must really love Jamie.

447
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,080
What are you talking about?

448
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:28,560
Oh?

449
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:32,160
You still don't realize

450
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:34,840
what the outcome of this war is?

451
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:57,360
Did you really think

452
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:59,840
the account of a random boy

453
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:02,000
playing with a dog every day

454
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:04,480
with nothing new or interesting

455
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:07,400
could reach 500,000 followers on its own?

456
00:37:11,160 --> 00:37:12,920
What you did

457
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:15,840
made everyone focus on Jamie

458
00:37:17,640 --> 00:37:20,960
because humans love conflict.

459
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:23,400
They love violence.

460
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,080
Right?

461
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:27,160
I won't accept that!

462
00:37:27,240 --> 00:37:29,800
<i>Without your hatred,</i>

463
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:32,560
<i>Jamie wouldn't have gotten</i>
<i>this much attention.</i>

464
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:38,920
It was fun.

465
00:37:44,160 --> 00:37:45,560
Very fun.

466
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:49,920
Fight them!

467
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:58,840
Fight them!

468
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:25,440
I finally found you.

469
00:38:28,040 --> 00:38:29,240
A stalker?

470
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:34,720
But you could only find me online, Sky.

471
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:37,560
Maybe not.

472
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,640
Go!

473
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,080
Anyway,

474
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:07,640
in the end,

475
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:11,960
this war ends with you being sacrificed.

476
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:15,000
But…

477
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:17,120
don't worry.

478
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:20,760
You've got plenty of fellow martyrs.

479
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:33,240
<i>Everyone,</i>

480
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:36,040
<i>I'm sorry for disappearing recently.</i>

481
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,760
<i>I was seriously sick.</i>

482
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:42,160
<i>But I'm getting better now,</i>

483
00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:44,480
<i>thanks to all of your support.</i>

484
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:49,600
<i>There's another thing</i>

485
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:51,720
<i>I want to tell everyone.</i>

486
00:39:51,800 --> 00:39:53,400
<i>Lately,</i>

487
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:56,720
<i>a group of people</i>
<i>has been trying to defame me.</i>

488
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,720
<i>So I've decided</i>

489
00:40:00,680 --> 00:40:02,480
<i>to sue both the ringleader,</i>

490
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,720
<i>whom I now know the identity of,</i>

491
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:06,880
<i>and all the followers involved.</i>

492
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:11,400
<i>At first, I hesitated,</i>
<i>not sure if I should sue.</i>

493
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:14,240
<i>But everyone told me</i>

494
00:40:14,320 --> 00:40:16,080
<i>I should set an example,</i>

495
00:40:17,200 --> 00:40:18,680
<i>so I have to do this.</i>

496
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:23,080
<i>Thank you all so much,</i>

497
00:40:23,160 --> 00:40:26,560
<i>including the people</i>
<i>who sent me information.</i>

498
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:28,680
<i>Hong says thank you too, right?</i>

499
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:30,160
<i>Thank the fans.</i>

500
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:32,560
PANGSTOP

501
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:39,200
{\an8}<i>You know that your support</i>

502
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:44,040
<i>is the best energy for me and Hong, right?</i>

503
00:41:21,200 --> 00:41:22,440
Five,

504
00:41:23,080 --> 00:41:24,280
four,

505
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:26,480
three,

506
00:41:27,160 --> 00:41:28,400
two,

507
00:41:29,480 --> 00:41:30,880
one.

508
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:39,080
Zero.

509
00:41:52,640 --> 00:41:54,280
Hongtae.

510
00:41:55,120 --> 00:41:59,080
You're the cutest anti-fan ever.

511
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:01,000
Did you know that?

512
00:42:40,200 --> 00:42:46,480
Jamie! Jamie!

513
00:43:40,600 --> 00:43:42,040
<i>It's my body.</i>

514
00:43:42,120 --> 00:43:44,520
<i>I can do whatever I want with it.</i>
<i>I can show whatever I want.</i>

515
00:43:45,880 --> 00:43:47,240
<i>It's my business.</i>

516
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:49,640
<i>My body, my choice.</i>

517
00:43:52,240 --> 00:43:54,000
The whole idea

518
00:43:54,080 --> 00:43:57,120
that our bodies belong to us

519
00:43:58,120 --> 00:43:59,680
is amazing.

520
00:44:02,520 --> 00:44:05,360
{\an8}<i>If you hadn't inspired me,</i>

521
00:44:05,920 --> 00:44:08,840
<i>we probably wouldn't be having</i>
<i>this much fun right now.</i>

522
00:46:05,640 --> 00:46:09,640
Subtitle translation by: Panuwat Baikeawon

